title: Suns Get Embarrassed, and Farewell Sasha | Real Ones
description:
Logan and Raja open the show with their reactions to the Phoenix Suns losing to an Australian basketball team, the Adelaide 36ers (02:00). Later, they briefly discuss expectations for James Wiseman this season (19:00), before bringing producer Sasha Ashall on to discuss all things Lakers (26:00).
Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
Guests: Sasha Ashall
Associate Producer: Jonathan Kermah
Production Assistant: Kai Grady
